{"tid":1425043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天琦師弟自願做港豬","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:36:21.000Z","uid":161551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"268e2b296e602d33c31ffab6b699711e644707d6","tid":1425043,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"借朋友Acc出Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話少講 直接上主菜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMember版：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公開版：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzHKzLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzHKzLu.png&h=ef883f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個同學既野，我忍唔住想問：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）爭取民主同埋自由變左做民粹主義同埋羊群效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n估唔到呢位同學你平時通識咁勁<br />\n點知<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">連一件事係點都未搞清楚</span></span><br />\n究竟佢有無聽過我地既五大訴求？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n究竟你係邊度見到民粹主義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2）黑衫係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7.21 元朗白衫恐襲事件<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警多次毆打市民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天水圍<span style=\"color: red;\">少女俾警察搞到走光</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天水圍13歲女學生被無故拘捕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察<span style=\"color: red;\">施放過期催淚彈</span></span><br />\n稱得上係暴徒既行為多到數唔曬<br />\n宜家係前線既人淨係放燃燒彈同埋Set路障<br />\n前線出手打人係因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人先撩者賤</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貨Van阿伯攞住把斧頭恐嚇前線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屯門電單車肥佬自己撞路障<br />\n咁究竟係咪示威者問題？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3）唔好阻我入U毀我未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n即使真係阻到你 都只不過係兩三日姐<br />\n你今年F.3咋 阻你一兩日就入唔到U？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打風夠阻到你啦 又唔見你鬧個風阻你入U？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4）沒有三餐溫飽 遑論民主自由</span></span><br />\n望下支那啦 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地有錢過你 日日大魚大肉 咁佢地有無自由啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5）你爭取民主 我爭取溫飽 有衝突咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n當你無左民主 法律就會俾人獨攬 如果獨攬大權既人所做既野係對你無益處或者對你不利嗰陣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你既生活 權利就一定會受到影響</span></span><br />\n假設第時香港取消最低工資 咁你既人工會點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個時候已經無民主 無人可以再發聲</span></span><br />\n到最後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你只會任人魚肉 連溫飽都無</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你作<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">為一個崇德學生 天琦係你同埋我既師兄</span></span> 我完全唔明點解到呢個時候 <span style=\"color: red;\">你都淨係顧住自己既未來</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出面有幾多同你差唔多大既人係度<ins><strong>食催淚彈 食子彈 俾棍打 俾人拉</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 你淨係見到我地阻住你 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實你出少日街係咪會死㗎？</span></span> 到呢一刻都仲話自己係中立 你係咪已經痴左線？<br />\n<br />\n係呢一刻仲話自己係中立既人 我想講：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你唔配做人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhUpzZu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhUpzZu.png&h=5700a63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你真係咁鍾意做港豬既，你繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果中國支那真係贏左 我同你都會一齊玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DC4hayt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDC4hayt.gif&h=d3394fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5199ffd76c724cac3ebc58f670d0df18a6db1c7","tid":1425043,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af2ee609f04faa14bd586065fa2772c849fb51d9","tid":1425043,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT